						               													<description>Troll Warband is a supplement for the Ragnarok: Age of Wolves miniatures wargame devoted an iconic monstrous race of the Mythic North that describes two varieties of Trolls, amphibious Meretrolls and savage Wolftrolls.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It includes eight sets of statistics that can be used together to form a complete new faction for the game or in conjunction with those for any other warriors and any sorts of scenarios. They include three named characters, including a giant ancient Meretroll, a half-Meretroll Wizard, and a half-Wolftroll warlord; two sorts of Meretroll followers; and two sorts of monsters, the Wolf Troll and Water Elemental. It also includes backstories for the various characters that describes their places in the marauding band of which they are part, as well as a new spell.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This book is supported by a set of Dwarf Soldiery Cardstock Characters miniatures that contains three variations on five different figures and a set of Dwarves: Tokens &amp;amp; Avatars for Virtual Tabletops. Contents of both of these sets correspond to the stats provided in this book and can be used with Ragnarok: Age of Wolves or any other tabletop or roleplaying games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ragnarok: Age of Wolves is a skirmish-level game for novice and experienced tabletop players alike that emulates desperate small-scale actions during the unending winter that is the first stage of the Viking Apocalypse.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
